## Quick Reference

```bash
# Check API health
curl http://localhost:8000/api/health

# Run endpoint tests
cd /data/dsa110-contimg/backend && bash test_api_endpoints.sh

# View API docs
open http://localhost:8000/api/docs

# Check systemd service
sudo systemctl status dsa110-api.service
```
